{
  "description": "A majestic waterfall cascades down a towering granite cliff face. The waterfall appears as a white ribbon against the dark grey rock, becoming more diffuse as it falls, creating a misty spray at its base. Dense green coniferous trees cover the lower slopes and the valley floor, providing a strong contrast to the granite. The cliff face itself is textured with vertical lines and patches of vegetation clinging to its surface. The sky is not directly visible, but the lighting suggests a clear, bright day. The scene evokes a sense of scale and natural power.",
